{
  "chapter": 163,
  "chapter_summary": "田猎最后一日，项少龙与鹿公在木寨外畅论将帅之道，鹿公以白起相比盛赞其治兵识人之能。宴会开始后，荆善不断传来高陵君和吕不韦方面的动向：高陵君的人在营帐浇火油，上游密林备好巨木筏子；吕不韦三百家将潜往泾水伏击，周子桓和鲁残分头行动。项少龙与昌平君、李斯分头部署，随后主动出击，先以言语震慑管中邪，再当面向莫傲揭穿飞龙宝枪和归燕之吻的秘密，以\"智者千虑必有一失\"和\"算人者人亦算之\"步步紧逼。莫傲毒发身亡，吕不韦方寸大乱。项少龙警告管中邪不得擅离，又以暗语嘲讽吕不韦，昂然离去。火光与喊杀声同时响起，小盘即位后的第一次叛乱正式爆发。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "白起之后，我大秦再无天资横溢的勇将，现在终于有了少龙，我亦老怀大慰。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lu_gong",
      "text": "鹿公切勿夸我，来秦之后，我尚未曾正式领军出征，何堪鹿公赞赏？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小处观人，最见真章。当年白起初出道时，亦像少龙般大小事情无有遗漏，人人折服，将士用命。少龙虽未正式征战沙场，但既能令上下人等均乐意为你效命，这正是作为一个名将的基本条件。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为将之道，首要治兵，只看少龙现在悠悠闲闲的样子，便知你深懂将帅之道。所谓纪律不严，何以能整？非练习娴熟，何以能暇？若非既整且暇，何以能万战万胜而无敌于天下乎？只看这几天少龙好整以暇的样子，就使我想起当年的白起。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "天生贤才，自是供一代之用。不患世无人，而患不知人；不患不知人，而患知人而不能用。少龙先后向储君推荐李斯、桓齮，又对王翦另眼相看，便可知少龙的眼光是如何高明，这方面恐怕白起都要逊你一筹。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_shan",
      "speaker_name": "荆善",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "高陵君的人开始把火油浇在寨后的营帐外，俊爷故意派人在附近巡逻，教他们只能在有限的营帐间做手脚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_shan",
      "text": "吕不韦的人有什么动静？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_shan",
      "speaker_name": "荆善",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕不韦的三百家将逐一离开营地，潜往泾水去，俊爷估计他们仍是采取在水中伏击的策略，当桥被冲断后，兵荒马乱之时，他的人自可为所欲为。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "兄弟！是时候了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看吕不韦的神色，似奇怪你的毒怎会仍未发作，嘿！真是有趣之极。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不过我仍不明白，吕不韦任得高陵君的人胡作非为，不怕玩火自焚，连自己都给人干掉吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "首先高陵君的手下中，必有吕不韦派去的内鬼，使吕不韦对高陵君的行动了如指掌；其次，吕不韦身边虽只得数百人，但他另外的一批从外地抽调回来的手下却可趁混乱掩来此处进行阴谋，加上到时我该已身亡，管中邪趁机把指挥权抢过去，那只要吕不韦傍在太后和储君身旁，又有莫傲给他出主意，谁敢不听他仲父的话呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "不冒点险，怎会有好的收成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "如此复杂的情况，我确是未曾想过。嘿！你看储君的精力多么旺盛，昨晚最多只睡了两、三个时辰，今天又忙了整天，现在仍是那么神气，先王比他差远哩！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_shan",
      "speaker_name": "荆善",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "依据灯号传讯，高陵君藏在上游密林的人已把巨木和筏子推进水里，只要营地火起，立即会配合攻来。周子桓和鲁残两人一个到了泾水去，另一个则离开营地，看来是要与另一批吕不韦的手下会合，俊爷已使人去跟踪他，若有异动，立杀无赦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_shan",
      "text": "是时候了，李大人立即去知会储君，我则过去找吕不韦弄些玩意儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "所有王族的内眷均被撤至安全地方，一切妥当，现在我去保护太后和储君，少龙小心了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "两位大人谈什么谈得这么兴高采烈呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "没有项大人在，说话总不够劲儿，来！我们喝两杯去！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "今晚明月晦暗，最利偷袭，我身负保安之责，不宜喝酒，这两杯管大人还是饶了我吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有项大人在，谁敢来偷营，必要栽个大跟斗。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "世事的离奇怪异，往往出人意表，所谓'人算不如天算'，管大人以为我这番话还有点道理吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙快来和我喝酒！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mo_ao",
      "text": "我今趟过来，是要向莫先生表示谢意。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_ao",
      "speaker_name": "莫傲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人为了何事要谢莫某人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙要谢莫先生什么事呢？我也心急想听听呀！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mo_ao",
      "text": "首先要谢的就是莫先生使醉风楼的伍孚先生赠我以飞龙，日后项少龙必以之驰骋沙场，以纪念莫先生餽赠宝物之德。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "落地开花，富贵荣华，好兆头，谨祝仲父长命百岁，身体健康。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_ao",
      "speaker_name": "莫傲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "伍孚楼主赠项大人宝枪，与我莫某人究竟有何关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mo_ao",
      "text": "智者千虑，必有一失，我只说伍孚赠我飞龙，却没有说是枪是剑，为何莫先生却知飞龙是宝枪呢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人第二件要谢莫先生的，又是什么事呢？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mo_ao",
      "text": "当然是归燕小姐深情一吻，莫先生尝惯美人香吻，当然比小弟更知个中滋味。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_ao",
      "speaker_name": "莫傲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mo_ao",
      "text": "时间差不多了，莫先生一向精于计算，对自己的生辰死忌当不会有失误。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mo_ao",
      "text": "算人者，人亦算之，莫先生明白这句话的意思吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "周子桓和鲁残两人到哪里去了？现在外面情况混乱，不要被人错手杀掉就好了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项统领这几句话是什么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_mo_ao",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "管大人最好不要离开这里，否则莫怪我以军法治你以擅离职守之罪。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "今晚月色暗晦，仲父走路过桥时小心点。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 163,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    }
  ],
